definitions.definition: Construction material supplied in sheets, and made of three or more layers of wood veneer glued together, laid up with alternating layers having their grain perpendicular to each other.
examples: After the hurricane there was a severe regional shortage of plywood , especially exterior plywood .

definitions.definition: A specific grade or type of this construction material.
examples: We stock exterior plywoods , interior plywoods , and furniture plywoods .

main_definition: ( uncountable ) Construction material supplied in sheets, and made of three or more layers of wood veneer glued together, laid up with alternating layers having their grain perpendicular to each other.
secondary_definitions: ( countable ) A specific grade or type of this construction material.
